INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID
INNER JOIN SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 ON COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER = SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID

    SELECT DISTINCT COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID
    FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias1
    INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias1 ON COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias1.COURSE_ID

    WHERE COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID
    GROUP BY SEMESTERalias1.SEMESTER
    HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT COURSEalias1.CREDITS) > 1
)

SELECT COURSE.DEPARTMENT, COURSE.NUMBER, AVG(STUDENT_RECORD.GRADE) AS AVERAGE_GRADE, COUNT(STUDENT_RECORD.STUDENT_ID) AS TOTAL_STUDENTS
FROM COURSE
JOIN STUDENT_RECORD ON COURSE.COURSE_ID = STUDENT_RECORD.COURSE_ID
GROUP BY COURSE.DEPARTMENT, COURSE.NUMBER
ORDER BY AVERAGE_GRADE DESC, TOTAL_STUDENTS DESC

    FROM student_record
    WHERE grade >= 2.0
)

WHERE department = "EECS" AND number >= 400 AND number < 500

    SELECT course_id
    FROM course_offering
    WHERE semester IN ('FA', 'WN') AND YEAR IN (2016, 2017)
)

AND (semester.semester = "FA" AND semester.year = 2016) 
OR (semester.semester = "WN" AND semester.year = 2017)

FROM course AS C1, course AS C2
